        -: 5759:	CODE:
        -: 5760:	{
        -: 5761:/* aoh2hoa($aoh) -- transpose an Array-of-Hashes into a Hash-of-Arrays.
        -: 5762:
        -: 5763: *   in : arrayref of hashrefs (rows)  [ {a=>1,b=>2}, {a=>3} ]
        -: 5764: *   out: hashref of arrayrefs (cols)  { a=>[1,3], b=>[2,undef] }
        -: 5765:
        -: 5766: * - Columns are the union of all row keys.
        -: 5767: * - Every column has exactly scalar(@$aoh) elements; cells absent
